e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future PLC/Lauren Bradbury)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eSince testing it out for myself, I’ve opted to keep it on all night, and I’ve slept right through with no sniffly midnight wake-ups and no stuffy nose in the morning. My husband, who suffers from severe hay fever symptoms (especially in March and early April), has also noticed that his eyes have become less and less itchy with each passing day.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut that’s not all. The sleek Scandi design is a standout feature in my eyes, and I’ve found it easy for what could be an eyesore appliance to blend into my \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom\"\u003ebedroom decor \u003c/a\u003e(which is more than I could say for the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/all-rooms/shark-neverchange5-air-purifier-review\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/all-rooms/shark-neverchange5-air-purifier-review\"\u003eShark NeverChange Air Purifier I tested recently\u003c/a\u003e, which offers a rather divisive design).\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHowever, what I love most about this bedroom air purifier is just how \u003cem\u003esilent \u003c/em\u003eit is. Although I’m used to the hum of appliances as one of \u003cem\u003eIdeal Home\u003c/em\u003e’s experts for all things home tech, my husband is extremely sensitive to night noises and has to have complete silence to fall asleep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-849pRVBgdtDh7VvCoQCgog\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u00