, as he’s always had to turn it off - sometimes after just ten minutes. But the hum of the Russell Hobbs Mini Aroma Air Purifier is so insignificant that the decibel meter on my phone couldn’t even detect it. Yes, it’s \u003cem\u003ethat \u003c/em\u003equiet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you find that essential oils help you \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/bedroom-advice/how-to-sleep-better-192220\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/bedroom-advice/how-to-sleep-better-192220\"\u003esleep better\u003c/a\u003e\u003cu\u003e,\u003c/u\u003e this air purifier also comes with an aromatherapy function to create a calming sleep environment. Just add a few drops of your favourite scent to the integrated diffuser pad to circulate in your bedroom as you sleep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-imageGallery-849pRVBgdtDh7VvCoQCgog-y1ezIui3MoDBjezfrnnrzjeY3YDydgYa\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eImage 1 of 2\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv aria-hidden=\"false\" data-swipeable=\"true\"\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture data-hydrate=\"true\"\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cKpKkNgDPRHuqRDrKx3crW-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cKpKkNgDPRHuqRDrKx3crW-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cKpKkNgDPRHuqRDrKx3crW-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cKpKkNgDPRHuqRDrKx3crW-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cKpKkNgDPRHuqRDrKx3crW-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cKpKkNgDPRHuqRDrKx3crW-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cKpKkNgDPRHuqRDrKx3crW-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cKpKkNgDPRHuqRDrKx3crW-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/cyclingnews/media/img/