03c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eSo far, I’ve been using this \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2FNEOM-Vibes-Essential-Blend-Scent%2Fdp%2FB08CJ9D69D%2F%3Fth%3D1%26tag%3Dhawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Didealhome-gb-1407996153197871328-21\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-url=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/NEOM-Vibes-Essential-Blend-Scent/dp/B08CJ9D69D/?th=1\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2FNEOM-Vibes-Essential-Blend-Scent%2Fdp%2FB08CJ9D69D%2F%3Fth%3D1%26tag%3Dhawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Dhawk-custom-tracking-21\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Amazon UK\" data-merchant-id=\"1027\" data-merchant-network=\"Amazon\" data-merchant-url=\"amazon.co.uk\"\u003eNEOM Feel Good Vibes Essential Oil Blend from Amazon\u003c/a\u003e, but I have my eyes on the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2FNEOM-Essential-Blend-Scent-Stress%2Fdp%2FB08B757WHW%2F%3Fth%3D1%26tag%3Dhawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Didealhome-gb-2215479781040586757-21\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-url=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/NEOM-Essential-Blend-Scent-Stress/dp/B08B757WHW/?th=1\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2FNEOM-Essential-Blend-Scent-Stress%2Fdp%2FB08B757WHW%2F%3Fth%3D1%26tag%3Dhawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Dhawk-custom-tracking-21\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Amazon UK\" data-merchant-id=\"1027\" data-merchant-network=\"Amazon\" data-merchant-url=\"amazon.co.uk\"\u003eNEOM Bedtime Hero Essential Oil Blend from Amazon\u003c/a\u003e to boost my sleep quality even more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe only thing I will say is that the lights on the top are a little annoying if you need a pitch-black bedroom to fall asleep (like myself). But I managed to solve this problem by laying a sock over the controls, making sure not to make an \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/all-rooms/what-causes-an-air-purifier-to-stop-working\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/all-rooms/what-causes-an-air-purifier-to-stop-working\"\u003eair purifier mistake\u003c/a\u003e and covering the vents at the top in the process.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlus, who can argue with this price point? Even at its recommended RRP of £49.99, this bedroom air purifier is considerably cheaper than other options on the market - but the 20% reduction for the Amazon Spring Deal Days event is the cherry on top.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-shop-similar-air-purifiers-for-bedrooms\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShop similar air purifiers for bedrooms\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"39fdbf22-2ae2-41a2-9243-77da8949cbbd\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2FRussell-Hobbs-Purifier-Allergies-RHAP1032WDB%2Fdp%2FB0CMXL2YRN%3Fth%3D1%26tag%3Dhawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Didealhome-gb-1094405295243394498-21\" data-model-name=\"Mini Aroma Air Purifier\" data-url=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Russell-Hobbs-Purifier-Allergies-RHAP1032WDB/dp/B0CMXL2YRN?th=1\" target=\"_blank\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=107653\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.uk%2FRussell-Hobbs-Purifier-Allergies-RHAP1032WDB%2Fdp%2FB0CMXL2YRN%3Fth%3D1%26tag%3Dhawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Dhawk-custom-tracking-21\" data-google-interstitial